Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0088898C\bord3\blur2\3c&H00FFFFFF\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs40\b1\pos(693.086,457.657)\frz16.45}还给你
